yd","tag-women-al-nisa"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-3z7","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":27596,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/15\/menses-missed-sawm-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":13709,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Menses: Women make up missed fasts, not prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adhah reported: I asked Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, \u201cWhy do menstruating women make up missed fasts but not missed prayers?\u201d Aisha said, \u201cWhen we were afflicted with menstruation, we were ordered to make up missed fasts but not missed prayers.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 335 Grade: Sahih (authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37044,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/09\/28\/hayd-fasts-not-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":13709,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Hayd: Menstruating women make up fasts, but not prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 28, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adhah reported: I asked Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, saying, \u201cWhy do menstruating women make up missed fasts but not missed prayers?\u201d Aisha said, \u201cWe endured those menses and we were ordered to make up missed fasts, but we were not ordered to make up missed prayers.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40536,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/07\/03\/women-hajj-menstruation\/","url_meta":{"origin":13709,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Menses: Women performing Hajj will menstruating","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 3, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, enter my dwelling at Sarif while I was crying. The Prophet said, \u201cWhat is the matter? Are you menstruating?\u201d I said yes. The Prophet said, \u201cThis is a matter that Allah has decreed for the daughters of Adam,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26807,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/09\/27\/shyness-seeking-knowledge\/","url_meta":{"origin":13709,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Shyness: Let not shyness stop you from seeking knowledge","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 27, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Safiyyah bint Shaybah reported: Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, said, \"How excellent are the women of the Ansar! They do not allow shyness to prevent them from understanding the religion.\" In another narration, Aisha said, \"They do not allow shyness to prevent them from asking questions about the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5047,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/12\/men-women-salat-al-eid\/","url_meta":{"origin":13709,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Eid: Women join men for Eid prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 12, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm 'Atiyyah reported: We were ordered to come out on the day of Eid, even the young girls and menstruating women from their houses. We would stand behind the men and declare the greatness of Allah along with them, and supplicate to Allah along with them, hoping for the blessings\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33902,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/01\/09\/prohibition-divorcing-menstruation\/","url_meta":{"origin":13709,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Talaq: Prohibition of divorcing women during menstruation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 9, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: He divorced his wife in the time of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, while she menstruating. Umar ibn al-Khattab asked the Prophet about that and he said, \u201cOrder him to return her. Let him leave her alone until she becomes pure, then\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13709","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts